[{"index":1,"title":"幻雨渊渟frigid","content":"&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;幻，幻想，梦幻，美好的字眼。但犹如羽毛一般飘着，落地了。幻灭。却永远只是一场梦。\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;在雨中，我看见梦的身影，依旧如飞燕一样，带着欢笑。只是幻影。\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;消失，因为幻……\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;幻雨，蒙蒙，但雨滴落地便不再起来。\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;渊渟，渊，渟，注定是静的澈水，也只是死水一潭。\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;再无以往的憧憬。\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;之所以飞，是要降落。\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;因为爱，才会恨。\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;我走过，匆匆……\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;寒冷的一切，凌冰，残雪，却仅为大自然泪的源泉。\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;飘……\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;幻雨渊渟。因为是寒冷的，所以冻结了记忆。我的故事没人记得，我还在等，等所有后悔的事淹灭。\r<br>Frigid，寒冷的世界。\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;我静静等待。\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;那些无缘的梦……&nbsp;\r<br>\u0018","author":"StarLight_幻","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.87b33dfd.XfFYg6NNc2pBOYRLu12fMQ&fr=pb","date":"2007-04-22 21:55","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":2,"title":"回复：幻雨渊渟frigid","content":"咳咳，赞~","author":"东少のforever","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.18d4b02a.fPHEXZieX7s93-Am-CmUSg&fr=pb","date":"2007-04-22 22:06","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":4,"title":"回复：幻雨渊渟frigid","content":"幻雨渊渟frigid......","author":null,"author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=&fr=pb","date":"2007-04-22 22:19","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null}]